%h2{class: "font-display text-xl font-bold text-ink mt-8 mb-3"} Account & More

%div{class: "flex flex-col gap-3"}
  %div{class: "v2-card"}
    %div{class: "font-semibold text-ink mb-2"} Q: I want to use serveme.tf in one of my own projects, is there an API?
    %em{class: "text-muted"}
      A: Yep! You can read how to use it
      = link_to("here.", "https://github.com/Arie/serveme/blob/master/README.md")
      Contact me for an API key, or get premium and look in your settings.

  %div{class: "v2-card"}
    %div{class: "font-semibold text-ink mb-2"} Q: How long do you store the demos/logs for a match?
    %em{class: "text-muted"}
      A: You can download the demos/logs zip for a reservation you created or played in for 21 days.

  %div{class: "v2-card"}
    %div{class: "font-semibold text-ink mb-2"} Q: I can't find my question in this FAQ
    %em{class: "text-muted"}
      A: Talk to us on
      = link_to "our Discord", 'https://discord.gg/0s38RdItLiCmARMm', :target => '_blank'
